reviews_data.review_text: Huge shout-out to Boaty, the unsung hero of my caffeine routine. Every time I walk in, he greets me like he’s been training his whole life for this moment. The man doesn’t just make drinks he crafts caffeinated masterpieces while radiating pure Starbucks spirit. If Starbucks had a Hall of Fame, Boaty would be the first inductee, no question.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi there! We're so glad you had a wonderful experience. Thanks for sharing it with us!

reviews_data.review_text: Great location and in the middle of a busy plaza for convenience. The interior is well- appointed resembling a European aesthetic, and the staff was exceptionally friendly and pleasant. A perfect location and atmosphere for a business meeting, with areas for intimate/private meetings.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hello! Thanks for taking the time to share this review. We appreciate you and look forward to having you back!

reviews_data.review_text: Tandem was amazing great customer service she even suggested different kinds of milk since I’m lactose but man she’s great thank you. Keep up the  good work

Yesterday I visited here for the very first time and I loved it. Boaty and Ruby were very friendly and made my visit delightful! Very welcoming and sweet with great conversation! The store was very clean and organized! My coffee was delicious without a doubt and I will definitely be back.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi there! We're so glad you had a wonderful experience. Thanks for sharing it with us!

reviews_data.review_text: Wasn’t as sweet as I would have liked my I’ve white Chocolate mocha to be
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hello! We're sorry to hear that your beverage was less than great. For future visits, please know that any Starbucks partner (employee) would be happy to remake your beverage at no additional cost. If you'd like to share this feedback with our team, please get in touch through our Contact Us page (https://sbux.co/3uW8Bbs)!

reviews_data.review_text: The service is always good and my drink is always right! But I will say this girl that works in there with curly hair and she draws on her eyebrows I’m sorry this is the only way to describe I think her name starts with an r and wears glasses. Completely ignored me she’s very rude. That is all. The girl with the brown/orange light blonde all mixed hair very good customer service skills!
